# COPILOT_GITHUB_TOKEN — GitHub PAT with Copilot access.
#
# Do NOT commit a real value. Two safer options:
#   1. macOS Keychain (recommended): run
#        node tests/01-keychain-store-token.mjs
#      then bring the stack up with
#        node tests/03-compose-up-with-keychain.mjs
#   2. Local-only .env (add `.env` to .gitignore first), then
#        docker compose --env-file .env up -d
COPILOT_GITHUB_TOKEN=
